image_analysis.description: A photograph of an open closet containing various shipping and packing supplies. On the top shelf, there are two large clear plastic bags filled with white packing peanuts. The middle shelf contains smaller items including rolls of tape and miscellaneous small objects. The floor of the closet holds several large cardboard boxes, including FedEx 'LARGE' and 'MEDIUM' boxes, and several tall rolls of brown and pink packing paper standing upright in a black bin and leaning against the wall.
image_analysis.layout: Interior closet view with shelving and floor storage.
